    "signatureHtml": "<kbd>/tikz/left delimiter=</kbd>⟨<i>delimiter</i>⟩",
    "defaultHtml": "(no default)",
    "snippetHtml": "<p> This option can be given to a any node that has the standard anchors <code>north</code>, <code>south</code> and so on. The ⟨<i>delimiter</i>⟩ can be any delimiter that is acceptable to TeX’s <code>\\left</code> command. </p>",
